## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in the criminal justice system. Additionally, the focus is primarily on the U.S. system, which may not fully represent global practices and challenges. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the system's fairness across different jurisdictions.